UNITED STATES ex rel. Vincenzo IERO, Relator Appellant, v. Henry H. CURRAN, as Commissioner, etc., Respondent Appellee. (Circuit Court of Appeals, Second Circuit. March 4, 1926.) No. 264. Gaspare M. Cusumano, of New York City, for appellant. Emory R. Buckner, U. S. Atty., of New York City (Nathan R. Margold, of New York City, Asst. U. S. Atty., of counsel), for appellee.

Before ROGERS, HOUGH, and MANTON, Circuit Judges.

PER CURIAM.

Order affirmed in open court.
